<section id="Sealing_a_Windows_7_or_Windows_2008_template" remap="TID_7571">
	<title>Sealing a Windows 7, Windows 2008, or Windows 2012 Template</title>
	<para>
		Seal a Windows 7, Windows 2008, or Windows 2012 template before using the template to deploy virtual machines.
	</para>
	<procedure>
		<title>Sealing a Windows 7, Windows 2008, or Windows 2012 Template</title> 
