			<para>
				The <application>Registry Editor</application> window opens. On the left pane, expand <menuchoice><guimenu>HKEY_LOCAL_MACHINE</guimenu><guisubmenu>SYSTEM</guisubmenu><guimenuitem>SETUP</guimenuitem></menuchoice>.
