		<step>
			<para>
				Launch <application>Sysprep</application> from <filename>C:\Windows\System32\sysprep\sysprep.exe</filename>.
			</para>
		</step>
		<step>
			<para>
				Enter the following information into the <application>Sysprep</application> tool:
			</para>
			<itemizedlist>
				<listitem>
					<para>
						Under <guilabel>System Cleanup Action</guilabel>, select <guilabel>Enter System Out-of-Box-Experience (OOBE)</guilabel>.
					</para>
				</listitem>
				<listitem>
					<para>
						Select the <guilabel>Generalize</guilabel> check box if you need to change the computer's system identification number (SID).
					</para>
				</listitem>
				<listitem>
					<para>
						Under <guilabel>Shutdown Options</guilabel>, select <guilabel>Shutdown</guilabel>.
					</para>
				</listitem>
			</itemizedlist>
		</step>
		<step>
			<para>
				Click <guibutton>OK</guibutton> to complete the sealing process; the virtual machine shuts down automatically upon completion.
			</para>
		</step>
	</procedure>
	<para>
		The Windows 7, Windows 2008, or Windows 2012 template is sealed and ready for deploying virtual machines.
	</para>
</section>
